### Payment Integration
- MercadoPago Integration: Complete payment gateway integration
- Subscription Creation: Automated subscription setup and management
- Payment Processing: Secure payment processing and validation
- Webhook System: Real-time payment status updates via webhooks
- Status Updates: Automated payment status synchronization
- Price Management: Dynamic subscription price updates
- Cancellation Process: Streamlined subscription cancellation
- Payment Methods: Support for both manual and automated payment options

